#OneStoryADay: I have been experimenting with drinks lately. I tend to play in the kitchen when I get overwhelmed. 

I haven't had soda for a number of years already, and I figured sparkling water is the next best thing. I watched tons of YouTube tutorials and found this recipe. 

As usual, I didn't take measurements. "Tantyametry" is the way to go. 😂😂😂

What about you? How are you coping?
